name: Matilda Jane Inspired Headband with Pinwheels in Pink, Yellow, Blue, Army Green & Purple
description:
Such an adorable and fun accessory - not to mention a great photo prop! With a fantastic yellow stretchy elastic band, this accessory will fit size infant to teenager. It would fit an adult with a small head as well :) Cute array of colored pinwheel type circles include colors of pink, yellow, purple, sky blue and army green. Sassy indeed!

The elastic band measures just under an inch in width. The pin wheel type circles measure about 2-2.25 inches in diameter each making the whole grouping about 3.5 x 4.5 inches. This headband is darling as is - but if you desire, you can embellish with your own creative whimsy - making a whole new look to sell in your own boutique or shop. The groundwork's been done for you!
